            26: "Being pressured by Smallweed for debt payment and by Tulkinghorn for letters. Refuses to give up letters out of loyalty to dead friend Hawdon.",
            27: "Visits Chesney Wold and has emotional reunion with his mother Mrs. Rouncewell after years of estrangement.",
